---
// src/components/index/Services.astro
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-3 font-semibold">What's Included</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-4">Everything Your Parish Needs</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-xl mx-auto text-lg">One platform. One price. Built specifically for Catholic parishes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">

      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold mb-2">Daily Liturgical Content</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Readings, feast days, saints, rosary mysteries — updated daily, automatically.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold mb-2">Mass Times</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Recurring schedules, special Masses, Holy Days, multiple churches.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v1m2 13a2 2 0 01-2-2V7m2 13a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m-4-3H9M7 16h6M7 8h6v4H7V8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold mb-2">Notices & Bulletin</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Deaths, baptisms, marriages, announcements, and weekly bulletin upload.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold mb-2">Sacraments & Directory</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Dedicated sacrament pages, clergy profiles, parish groups, and schools.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold mb-2">Online Donations</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Secure giving powered by Stripe. One-off and recurring.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-bold mb-2">Livestream</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">YouTube, ChurchServices.tv or any provider. Broadcast schedule included.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-14">
      <a href="/services" class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors inline-block text-sm">
        See All Features
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
